name: Morning Glee
description:
Don't you love those mornings when everything feels just great? When it feels like the start to a perfect day? I hope this reminds you of those moments, now that they don't seem to come by so often.

Hand drawn loop animation 850x1200px GIF. For personal, non-commercial use only.
